Author: SupplyBloc
Title: [ANN] [STO] [SUPX] SupplyBloc Technology - Revolutionizing Global Supply Chains
Body: Announcing the SUPX Token Sale from SupplyBloc Technology!   UPDATE: Demonstrating leadership in the market, SupplyBloc, Inc. has voluntarily paused its pre-STO Offering while it prepares appropriate Registration Statement(s) with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission. The filing(s) will give our STO token purchasers greater security throughout the token buying process as well as comfort knowing that SupplyBloc, Inc. has gone the extra mile to comply with proposed SEC requirements.  The ever-changing landscape of STO regulations has created many challenges. SupplyBloc, Inc. believes in meeting the challenges head on, complying with proposed regulations and maintaining the utmost transparency for the benefit of our token purchasers.  Rest assured, we will move forward with our pre-STO and STO Offering as soon as this process is complete. We encourage you to monitor our website for updates.  Thank you.
